title: Kundalini Activation [custom mix]
description:
This is a hypnosis/brain entrainment combination that I made for myself, but it was so useful that I thought I'd share it with you guys.

My disclaimer is, if your head implodes from using this, or anything similar, I had nothing to do with it ...

And what is Kundalini Activation? If you don't know, you're in the wrong place. Try http://www.biologyofkundalini.com/ first.

The hypnotic track is actually two tracks playing simultaneously. They're both daytime affirmations by Steve G Jones, playing at different speeds.

The brain entrainment track is an oldie but goodie, Deep Mind VI.

Enjoy.
